<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٧٤٥ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَيُّوبَ قَالَ:</span> سُئِلَ مُجَاهِدٌ عَنْ أَكْلِ الْقِرْدِ؟<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ مِنْ بَهِيمَةِ الْأَنْعَامِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>